---
title: Creamy Pesto , Chicken Breasts and Cheese Rigatoni with Crispy Bacon and Veggies
description: This pasta dish doesn't want the good weather to end, with creamy basil pesto, corn and Parmesan bringing the summer vibes. A little sprinkle of bacon and sliced chicken at the end ties the whole dish together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rigatonis-au-fromage-aux-poitrines-de-poulet-et-au-pesto-cremeux-a6b403bb.jpg
